WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.137
At its core, myocarditis is an

00:00:03.137 --> 00:00:05.751
inflammatory injury to the myocardium.

00:00:05.751 --> 00:00:08.889
A precipitating insult — typically viral,

00:00:08.889 --> 00:00:12.026
autoimmune, or toxic — triggers lymphocytic

00:00:12.026 --> 00:00:12.549
infiltration.

00:00:12.549 --> 00:00:15.686
A cytokine cascade then drives myocyte

00:00:15.686 --> 00:00:18.300
necrosis and progressive fibrotic remodeling.
